Package: ltapi
Title: Fetch data from LimnoTrack API and web services
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Tadhg", "Moore", , "tadhg@limnotrack.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3834-8868")),
    person("Chris", "McBride", , "chris@limnotrack.com", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Provides a tidy interface to the LimnoTrack PostgREST API
    (<https://api.limnotrack.com/postgrest>), enabling R users to explore,
    filter, and retrieve lake and water quality data directly into their R
    session. Tables with geometry columns are automatically returned as 'sf'
    objects. Includes helpers for constructing filter expressions using
    familiar R syntax, in-session schema caching to minimise API calls, and
    informative error messages for common failure modes such as unavailable
    endpoints or missing tables.
